title: Pixel Probe
des: GDSC UMIT proudly presents 'Pixel Probe' our Medium page and blog series where students share their insights and experiences related to various technologies.

title: SpaceSprint Hackathon
des: In collaboration with IEEE UMIT, GDSC UMIT recently hosted a hackathon for students of UMIT. It provided an platform for students to showcase their skills.

title: Google Cloud Study Jam
des: GDSC UMIT  hosted a session to introduce students to the Google Cloud Study Jam program and its benefits. Students also won goodies.

title: Hacktober Fest
des: GDSC organized an enlightening session to introduce students to the vibrant world of open-source contribution through the renowned event, Hacktoberfest.

title: Solution Challenge
des: GDSC UMIT hosted an engaging session to introduce students to the Solution Challenge Program, an exciting opportunity for budding innovators.

title: Industrial visit
des: The GDSC UMIT organized an enriching industrial visit to Capgemini, a pioneer in the corporate world.
